                      </div>
                      <p style="margin:0 0 10px; font-size:12px; line-height:1.7; color:var(--text-gray);">
                        ガソリン・保険・駐車場・整備の合計。先月より
                        <strong style="color:#cf1f77;">+0.6万円</strong>です。
                      </p>
                      <div class="graph" style="height:100px;">
                        <div class="graph-bubble" id="trendBubble">6か月後査定 286万円予測</div>
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 300 90" fill="none" aria-label="維持費と将来予測グラフ">
                          <path d="M10 54 C 38 44, 66 46, 92 40 C 120 34, 146 30, 172 30 C 208 30, 238 24, 290 20" stroke="rgba(29,220,255,0.18)" stroke-width="18" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                          <path d="M10 54 C 38 44, 66 46, 92 40 C 120 34, 146 30, 172 30 C 208 30, 238 24, 290 20" stroke="#33bdf9" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                          <path d="M10 76 C 54 74, 86 66, 118 64 C 164 60, 214 52, 290 38" stroke="#F84CA2" stroke-width="4" stroke-dasharray="7 7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                        <div class="graph-labels">
                          <span>維持費</span>
                          <span>相場推移</span>
                          <span>売り時</span>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="ring">
                      <div class="ring-center">
                        <strong id="ringValue">4.8</strong>
                        <span>万円 / 月</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="legend">
                    <div class="legend-item">
                      <span class="legend-left"><span class="dot" style="background:#F84CA2;"></span>ガソリン</span>
                      <strong id="gasolineCost">1.5万円</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="legend-item">
                      <span class="legend-left"><span class="dot" style="background:#ffbc66;"></span>保険</span>
                      <strong id="insuranceCost">1.2万円</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="legend-item">
                      <span class="legend-left"><span class="dot" style="background:#63d5ff;"></span>駐車場</span>
                      <strong id="parkingCost">1.4万円</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="legend-item">
                      <span class="legend-left"><span class="dot" style="background:#b9c0df;"></span>整備・洗車</span>
                      <strong id="maintCost">0.7万円</strong>
